key points 
ERC-20 standard → Works with wallets, DEXs, explorers.
Total supply fixed → 10,000,000,000 POPS × 18 decimals.
Minting disabled → Only initial supply minted.
Burn functions → Community and optional owner burn, keeps token deflation optional.
Ownable → You (the deployer) control the contract initially. Can later renounce ownership to prove decentralization.
